{"tid":333934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【迷魂黨出沒？】內地女中環行過撞一撞 港男一索濃烈異味即頭暈","createTime":"2017-07-24T09:30:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T10:12:29.000Z","uid":30561,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b7c131c2b51aec55526406662d8af8a3b9313578","tid":333934,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T09:30:33.000Z","msg":"晚上6時許，一名35歲姓顏男子報稱在中環環球大廈附近與一內地女子發生碰撞，其間他嗅到一陣濃烈的氣味後感到頭暈，於是向附近的食環署職員求助報警。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報趕到，但發現事主所指的女子已離去，經調查後相信共有兩女一男操普通話的疑人涉案，案發時他們曾向男事主揮動一紙巾，事主吸入氣味後感不適。男事主並無損失，惟需送院治理。案件暫列危害生命或使人身體受嚴重傷害而使用毒藥，交由中區刑事調查隊第一隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170723/56993851\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170723%2F56993851&d=AL4ZPfA3YmWAvnWY7nhRZdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=b1178b8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170723%2F56993851&h=e5c03d5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170723/56993851</a>"},{"pid":"e15a4d3b032d580b25014eaf0c69c5f39126df64","tid":333934,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T10:12:29.000Z","msg":"臭閪"}]}